tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE UserActions (
    user_id UUID,
    action_type VARCHAR(50),
    action_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    action_details JSON,
    PRIMARY KEY (user_id, action_timestamp)
)

CREATE TABLE DeviceInteractions (
    device_id UUID,
    device_type VARCHAR(50),
    action_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    PRIMARY KEY (device_id, action_timestamp)
)

CREATE TABLE SessionLogs (
    session_id UUID,
    user_id UUID,
    session_start TIMESTAMP,
    session_end TIMESTAMP,
    PRIMARY KEY (session_id)
)

CREATE TABLE SceneInteractions (
    scene_id UUID,
    user_id UUID,
    action_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    PRIMARY KEY (scene_id, action_timestamp)
)

CREATE TABLE user_profiles (
    user_id INT,
    first_name VARCHAR,
    last_name VARCHAR,
    email VARCHAR,
    age INT,
    country VARCHAR
);
